Text:
Thanks for this. 

Is this the version of the show that has the janitor / invisible drumkit sketch at the end?

Some releases do not have this (a shame too, because it's awesome).

Unfortunately this doesn't have the drum sketch at the end. But it does have 3 sketches I haven't seen before(at least on the USA version tape); 
"Elementary Dating", "Guys after the Game" and "Thomas, Richard and Harold".  Great stuff, thanks for the upload, I haven't seen this since my friend "lost" my old tape.
